dct_title_s: Plan of Proposed Road Fortescue Downe Twp. Cumb. Co.
dct_description_sm: Downe Township between Garrison Avenue and Downe Avenue along Fortescue Creek.
The proposed new road and the road used now is shown on the map. Boat berths are marked. The land of the State of New Jersey and of H. Garrison Est. are shown on the map.
